{"about_the_game":"One night, you receive an origami letter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn the front of the letter was written in four large characters, &quot;Honor your fist guessing,&quot; and signed in &quot;silver&quot;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe contents of the letter were strange, a few crude pictures and a few short lines.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou did not think much, in the computer desk before the ambush case is too long, gradually sleep......<br />\r\n<br />\r\n......<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHowever, the picture of the letter in your mind, is becoming more and more clear.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nps.<br />\r\nThe game is a story-driven role-playing game in which you enter a fantasy world of &quot;guess-guessing&quot; using an origami letter.<br />\r\nIn the game, you will learn about scissors, rock, paper, these three gestures behind the three large doors, and the earthshaking power of guessing-fist in the ancient times.<br />\r\nThe story, the puzzle, the adventure, what unknowns and dreams lie ahead?<br />\r\nGo for it, your guess-guessing journey is about to begin","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1636356925","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641410/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1636356925","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641410/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1636356925","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1641410/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1636356925","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"One night, you receive an origami letter.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn the front of the letter was written in four large characters, &quot;Honor your fist guessing,&quot; and signed in &quot;silver&quot;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe contents of the letter were strange, a few crude pictures and a few short l